data.description: Welcome Home! The open layout of this move-in ready home will not disappoint. The well-appointed kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances, is an ideal space for cooking and entertaining. The spacious master bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and an ample master bath. Down the hall, you will find another comfy bedroom and a full classic bathroom. Downstairs, the enticing three bedrooms, a full bath and a movie room made for evenings of fun and relaxation will be the basis for guests and memories to come. The three car garage has plenty of space for storage and parking while the fenced backyard is where you will enjoy your morning coffee and evening barbecues.
